If interviewer asks:

Explain API Gateway vs Service Mesh

You say:

> API Gateway manages client-to-service communication and acts as the entry point for external requests. Service mesh manages service-to-service communication inside the system and provides features like retries, load balancing, and observability.



This is a very strong answer.


